        <details class="pf-faq-item"><summary><span class="pf-faq-tag pf-tag-orange">COST</span>&nbsp; How much does an emergency plumber cost in Aintree?</summary><div class="pf-faq-body"><p>Fixed hourly rates: weekdays 9am to 5pm £80/hr, weekends 9am to 1pm £120/hr, out of hours nights and bank holidays £150/hr. All have a 1 hour minimum. Parts charged at cost. Most jobs cost between £80 and £350. Written quote before work begins. No separate call-out fee.</p></div></details>
